      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an impeccable E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example boasts a documented Vanos overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring peak reciprocating assembly health. The chassis is structurally flawless with proactive subframe reinforcement, preserving its legendary torsional rigidity. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Finished in collector-grade condition, the suspension geometry remains true with zero bushing compliance issues, delivering a visceral, analog driving experience that meets the most stringent mechanical standards.",
